TITLE: Manually Controlling Session Replay Recording in React Native
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to manually start and stop Session Replay recording by using the startRecordingImmediately parameter and control methods.
SOURCE: https://github.com/datadog/dd-sdk-reactnative/blob/develop/packages/react-native-session-replay/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { SessionReplay } from "@datadog/mobile-react-native-session-replay";

SessionReplay.enable({
  replaySampleRate: sampleRate,
  startRecordingImmediately: false
});
// Do something
SessionReplay.startRecording();
SessionReplay.stopRecording();
```

