SOURCE: https://github.com/datadog/dd-sdk-reactnative/blob/develop/packages/react-native-apollo-client/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { ApolloClient, HttpLink } from '@apollo/client';

// before
